Title : Ghrelin O-acyltransferase
Text : {{Infobox_gene}}
'''Ghrelin O-acyltransferase''' also known as '''membrane bound O-acyltransferase domain containing 4''' is an [[enzyme]] that in humans is encoded by the MBOAT4 [[gene]].<ref name="entrez">{{cite web | title = Entrez Gene: Membrane bound O-acyltransferase domain containing 4 | url = https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/gene/619373 }}</ref>
It is homologous to other [[MBOAT|membrane-bound O-acyltransferases]].

